  "name": "RPlog_Soren_Face_Lift",
  "title": "An M for Mailyn",
  "summary": "On a Tatooine landing field, the Force-user Simon recovers from a stun blast just in time to watch the Sable Seraph lift off with the abducted Lady Mailyn Raines aboard. Blaming the cowardly Viscount Soren for sabotaging Mailyn's ship, Simon recalls his wooden staff to his hand through the Force and pursues the fleeing, portly nobleman across the tarmac, knocking him down with the thrown staff and his fists. Soren manages one desperate, ineffective swing that cracks one of Simon's ribs, but Simon, wrapped in cold rage and the power of the True Source, pins him to the ground. Declaring that he loves Mailyn, Simon ignites his green lightsaber and carves the letter 'M' into the screaming Viscount's face before Soren passes out from the pain. The mad fury spent, Simon walks away, disturbed to find he feels no regret for his cruelty, only curiosity.",
